        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="testimonial-item mx-auto mb-5 mb-lg-0">
          <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle mb-3 px-5" src="img/2.jpg" alt="">
          <h5>Fred S.</h5>
          <p class="font-weight-light mb-0">
            "Thanks so much for opening up the world to us!"
          </p>
